name: Nucleic acid sequence alignment
synonyms: ["Sequence alignment (nucleic acid)","RNA sequence alignment","DNA sequence alignment"]

name: Nucleic acid sequence record

name: Image

name: Annotation track
description: Annotation of one particular positional feature on a biomolecular (typically genome) sequence, suitable for import and display in a genome browser.
synonyms: ["Genome-browser track","Genome annotation track","Genomic track","Genome track","Sequence annotation track"]
